# Component & Layout Rules

These components are **shared and considered stable**. Reuse them as-is.
Do not restyle, restructure, or "improve" them as a side effect of an
unrelated task. Only change them when the user explicitly asks, and only the
specific thing they ask for ŌĆö never bundle in extra tweaks.

## Stability contract (do NOT change without explicit instruction)

| Component | File | Locked aspects |
|-----------|------|----------------|
| `TopNav` | `src/components/TopNav.tsx` | DOM order `brand ŌåÆ nav ŌåÆ account`; all three are direct siblings of `.site-header-inner`. Do not re-nest. |
| Brand | `.brand`, `.brand-logo`, `.brand-wordmark` | Logo/wordmark `clamp()` sizing and ratio. |
| Nav links | `.nav-link`, `.nav-link--active` | Padding, color, active state. |
